&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Sonder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;At Sonder, we believe every person deserves to feel safe, supported, and empowered to be at their best, wherever they are. We&#39;re redefining workplace health, safety, and wellbeing through a seamless blend of technology and human expertise. Sonder&#39;s mobile platform provides 24/7, real-time support from a dedicated team of safety, medical, and mental health professionals, ensuring members receive immediate care when they need it most. In critical situations, we go beyond digital support, offering on-the-ground assistance to manage time-sensitive incidents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;We&#39;re also actively building toward an AI-native organisation, using real-time insights to help organisations take proactive steps toward a healthier, safer future with direct, measurable impact on the bottom line.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Since our founding in 2017, we&#39;ve grown rapidly across Australia, New Zealand, and the UK. Backed by Seek and Blackbird, we support over one million members and 200+ team members globally. We&#39;re well-capitalised, scaling fast, and the work we do genuinely matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;This is a rare hire. We&#39;re looking for a Chief of Staff who operates as a true strategic partner and force multiplier for our CEO, someone who brings the clinical credibility to understand our product at its core, the commercial rigour of top-tier consulting, and the operational instinct to move fast in a scaling health-tech company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;This is not a Chief of Staff role for someone transitioning into strategy. You&#39;ll need deep foundations in all three areas: clinical training, MBB-calibre commercial experience, and a track record of post-clinical leadership to be effective in this seat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Own Sonder&#39;s government affairs and regulatory strategy, positioning us as a leader in responsible AI, digital health, and clinical governance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Partner directly with the CEO to identify and land growth opportunities, including new products, GTM motions, and international market entry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Serve as the connective tissue between the CEO and the Executive Leadership Team, ensuring alignment on strategic priorities and trade-offs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Act as a trusted extension of the CEO, preparing board and investor materials, accompanying them on domestic and international travel, and ensuring they&#39;re briefed for every critical engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot

&lt;p&gt;Sonder is an Australian-founded employee care platform that gives organisations a single place to support their people’s health, mental wellbeing, and personal safety. Rather than routing employees through fragmented services. Sonder unifies medical advice, mental health support, and safety assistance in one 24/7 mobile app.&amp;nbsp;Employees access the platform directly from their phone. When they reach out, they are connected to real clinicians, nurses, psychologists, and social workers via live chat or phone, typically within 30 seconds. The platform is available around the clock, every day of the year.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sonder is headquartered in Sydney and also operates in New Zealand and the United Kingdom. It is the first technology company to have achieved accreditation from the Australian Council on Healthcare Standards (ACHS), placing it alongside leading hospitals and healthcare institutions in Australia and globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An Exciting Time to Join Sonder!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Since our founding in 2017, Sonder has experienced rapid growth, expanding operations across Australia, New Zealand, and the UK. Backed by Australia’s leading venture capital firms, Seek and Blackbird, we are well-capitalised and on a mission to scale globally, partnering with corporations, educational institutions, and government agencies to transform workplace wellbeing at scale.&lt;br&gt;That ambition extends to how we run the business. Sonder is actively building toward an AI-native organisation, where automation and intelligent tooling are embedded into how every function operates.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our impact and scale:&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 1,000,000+ members across multiple countries&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 200+ team members, plus an extensive network of on-the-ground responders&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you’re passionate about using technology and human expertise to drive meaningful change, join us in shaping the future of workplace wellbeing!&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our Company Values&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; We focus on impact&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; We choose action over perfection&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; We navigate the minefields&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; We deliver a four-quarter effort&lt;br&gt;● &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; We are on the journey together&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join Sonder’s mission to deliver timely and effective global support, and contribute to empowering people to be at their best.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;161&quot; data-end=&quot;445&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a highly organised and commercially minded Customer Renewals Manager to join Sonder on a 6-month fixed-term contract. This role sits at the heart of our Customer team, owning the end-to-end renewal and seat expansion process across our Tech Touch customer portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;447&quot; data-end=&quot;850&quot;&gt;Working in a fast-paced, high-growth environment, you&#39;ll play a critical role in protecting recurring revenue, driving customer growth opportunities, and ensuring our commercial operations run seamlessly. If you&#39;re someone who thrives on process, enjoys working with data and systems, and takes pride in delivering high-quality outcomes, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Owning the end-to-end renewal process for a high-volume portfolio of customer accounts, ensuring all renewals are completed accurately and on time&lt;br data-start=&quot;1026&quot; data-end=&quot;1029&quot;&gt;• Identifying a

&lt;p&gt;At Sonder, we believe that every person deserves to feel safe, supported, and empowered to be at their best - wherever they are. That’s why we’re redefining workplace health, safety, and wellbeing through a seamless blend of technology and human expertise. Sonder’s mobile platform provides 24/7, real-time support from a dedicated team of safety, medical, and mental health professionals - ensuring that our members receive immediate care when they need it most. In critical situations, we go beyond digital support, offering on-the-ground assistance to manage time-sensitive incidents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By harnessing real-time insights, we enable organisations to take proactive steps toward a healthier, safer future, which leads directly to tangible bottom-line business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An Exciting Time to Join Sonder!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since our founding in 2017, Sonder has experienced rapid growth, expanding operations across Australia, New Zealand, and the UK. Backed by Australia’s leading venture capital firms, Seek and Blackbird, we are well-capitalised and on a mission to scale globally, partnering with corporations, educational institutions, and government agencies to transform workplace wellbeing at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our impact and scale:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1,000,000+ members across multiple countries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;200+ team members, plus an extensive network of on-the-ground responders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re passionate about using technology and human expertise to drive meaningful change, join us in shaping the future of workplace wellbeing!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;185&quot; data-end=&quot;498&quot;&gt;The Executive Assistant as Sonder is a key partner to the CEO, providing reliable and professional support to ensure time, priorities, and operations are managed efficiently. You will also support the wider Executive Team, coordinating critical tasks and reducing administrative load to help leaders focus on what matters most.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;500&quot; data-end=&quot;870&quot;&gt;To succeed in this role, you’ll bring deep experience supporting senior executives, exceptional attention to detail, and the ability to stay composed under pressure. You’ll be highly proficient in Google Workspace, confident in preparing polished board-level presentations, and comfortable using modern tools, including AI, to deliver efficient, high-quality outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;617&quot; data-end=&quot;723&quot;&gt;Manage and optimise complex calendars, balancing competing priorities across the CEO and Executive Team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;726&quot; data-end=&quot;840&quot;&gt;Coordinate high-stakes meetings, board sessions, investor interactions, and external engagements with precision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;843&quot; data-end=&quot;971&quot;&gt;Draft, edit, and refine executive communications, reports, and board-level presentations to the highest professional standard.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;974&quot; data-end=&quot;1087&quot;&gt;Anticipate challenges, resolve scheduling conflicts, and streamline workflows to maximise executive efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1090&quot; data-end=&quot;1199&quot;&gt;Plan and execute domestic and international travel and events, ensuring seamless itineraries and logistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1202&quot; data-end=&quot;1314&quot;&gt;Leverage digital and AI tools to enhance research, automate tasks, and deliver efficient, data-driven outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1317&quot; data-end=&quot;1405&quot;&gt;Uphold absolute discretion in handling sensitive matters and confidential information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;140

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Sonder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Sonder, we believe every person deserves to feel safe, supported, and empowered to be at their best, wherever they are. We&#39;re redefining workplace health, safety, and wellbeing through a seamless blend of technology and human expertise. Sonder&#39;s mobile platform provides 24/7, real-time support from a dedicated team of safety, medical, and mental health professionals, ensuring members receive immediate care when they need it most.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since our founding in 2017, we&#39;ve grown rapidly across Australia, New Zealand, and the UK. Backed by Seek and Blackbird, we now support over one million members and 200+ team members globally. We&#39;re well-capitalised, scaling fast, and actively building toward an AI-native organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-ownership finance role at a critical point in Sonder&#39;s growth. Reporting to the Financial Controller, you&#39;ll take full accountability for the financial controllership engine: month-end close, statutory compliance, audit, and payroll oversight across three jurisdictions, while dedicating roughly half your time to process improvement and finance transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role exists to ensure the day-to-day runs with minimal oversight, giving the FC capacity to focus on systems architecture and broader transformation. If building an AI-native finance function is genuinely part of what you&#39;re looking for, this is the right place and role for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end month-end close process across AU, NZ, and UK entities, consistently delivered within five business days and to a high standard without close direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead annual audit preparation across all entities, acting as the primary contact for the external audit team, managing timelines, and preparing draft statutory financial statements for FC review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide review and sign-off on fortnightly payroll across all three jurisdictions, maintaining compliance with local employment obligations and acting as the primary finance contact for payroll escalations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own all statutory compliance obligations including BAS/GST/VAT, payroll taxes, and employer returns, maintaining a forward-looking compliance calendar and ensuring no deadline is missed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive a prioritised process improvement roadmap in partnership with the FC, owning execution end-to-end from process mapping through to embedding, including meaningful contribution to Sonder&#39;s planned ERP transition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee accounts payable, expense platform administration, and cashflow visibility to support FC and CFO decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CA/CPA qualified with a minimum of eight years post-qualification experience, including at least three years in a corporate finance environment operating at a senior level with minimal oversight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ownership of a month-end close process and direct experience leading an external audit end-to-end, including preparation of audit files and statutory financial statements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated track record of identifying and implementing process improvements through technology or automation - this is a core requirement, not a nice-to-have&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence managing compliance obligations across multiple jurisdictions without close direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort working in and actively improving a systems environment; experience with Xero is an advantage, as is familiarity with Subscript and Aleph&lt;/li&gt;
