&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;Customer Insights and Measurement&lt;/strong&gt; team at Sonder is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Full Stack Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to help us build the next generation of wellbeing intelligence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own the end-to-end journey of turning raw data into intelligent insights. On any given week, you might be building React-based dashboards, optimizing Snowflake transformations, or architecting multi-agent workflows that help our customers &quot;talk&quot; to their safety data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Sonder, &quot;Health and Wellbeing&quot; isn&#39;t just a benefit; it’s our product. You’ll be building the tools that measure human impact, helping us move from reactive support to proactive, data-driven actions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
