&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Stack Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Ownership: &lt;/strong&gt;Build and maintain features from the database schema and Snowflake models through to the React UI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;API Architecture: &lt;/strong&gt;Design robust back-end services (Python/Node.js) that support data ingestion and high-concurrency reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Pipelines &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Engineering Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Design and optimize tables, views, and complex query workloads in &lt;strong&gt;Snowflake&lt;/strong&gt; to keep compute overhead low and dashboard latency fast.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transformation:&lt;/strong&gt; Build scalable, maintainable data transformation pipelines to establish an accurate, single source of truth for all reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Integration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insight Automation:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage LLMs to transform complex workplace metrics into actionable executive summaries and power interactive agents for our B2B customers.&lt;/li&gt;
