&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sonder is looking for a General Counsel and Company Secretary to lead our legal function at a pivotal point in the company&#39;s growth. Reporting to the CFO, you&#39;ll manage a team of two Legal Counsel and oversee our external counsel relationships, while acting as Company Secretary to the Board, running Board meetings, governance and investor relations end to end.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the centre of Sonder&#39;s push to become an AI-native organisation, you&#39;ll design new legal and company secretary workflows built around AI, and work across Sales, Product and Customer Success to make our contracting process faster and simpler for everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
