&lt;p data-start=&quot;1150&quot; data-end=&quot;1431&quot;&gt;This is a standalone role with significant autonomy and influence. You&#39;ll be responsible for developing and executing the partnership strategy, identifying new opportunities, nurturing existing relationships and creating a scalable pipeline that supports our Enterprise sales team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1433&quot; data-end=&quot;1728&quot;&gt;As part of this role, you&#39;ll work closely with Account Executives to develop and progress opportunities through complex, multi-stakeholder sales cycles, helping organisations improve employee health, safety and wellbeing outcomes while reducing workers&#39; compensation claims and associated costs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1730&quot; data-end=&quot;1935&quot;&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for an experienced commercial professional who enjoys building relationships, navigating complex sales environments and creating new growth opportunities from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
