&lt;p&gt;As Sonder’s Product Marketing Lead, you’ll lead Sonder’s go-to-market (GTM) strategy for new and existing products and solutions. Reporting to the Head of Marketing, you’ll connect the dots between customer needs, market insights, and Sonder’s evolving product suite — shaping positioning, messaging, and launch strategies that drive growth and differentiation. This is a highly cross-functional and strategic role, working closely with teams across Product, Growth and Commercial to bring new features and solutions to market, ensure internal teams are enabled with the right tools and narratives, and craft clear, compelling stories that connect Sonder’s capabilities to customer value and business outcomes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;You’ll lead end-to-end go-to-market (GTM) strategy and execution for new and existing products and solutions — defining how Sonder is positioned, communicated, and brought to market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and own product positioning, messaging, and value propositions across solution pillars.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead GTM planning and execution for product and solution launches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate customer insights and market trends into actionable strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product and Commercial teams to align product releases with business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Creative and Growth teams to develop launch assets and campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support thought leadership initiatives and case studies that strengthen Sonder’s market presence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure and optimise GTM performance, using data to refine strategy and impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
