&lt;li&gt;Conduct six online counselling sessions per day&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with members from diverse backgrounds, providing culturally safe and inclusive support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist members in developing self-regulation strategies and achieving their mental health goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult with internal and external health and wellbeing providers to implement individualised care plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and comprehensive case notes in compliance with best practice standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in regular clinical supervision, training, and quality assurance activities to ensure high professional standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
