&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has a growth mindset and is passionate, self-motivated, and takes pride in producing high-quality work every day. Above all else, you - the ideal candidate - will embody the Sonder values and love working in a fast-paced, dynamic workplace.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
